---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="page-container">
		<div class="page-header">
			<h1>Testimonials</h1>
			<p class="page-subtitle">What Our Readers Say About Akboheim</p>
		</div>

		<div class="page-content">
			<section class="intro-section">
				<p>
					We are honored to serve a community of passionate readers, writers, and thinkers who share our love for literature, culture, and education. Here are some of the thoughtful words from our readers about their experience with Akboheim.
				</p>
			</section>

			<div class="testimonials-grid">
				<div class="testimonial">
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							"Akboheim has become my go-to source for thoughtful literary criticism. The depth of analysis and clarity of writing consistently exceed my expectations. Each essay feels like a conversation with a well-read friend who genuinely cares about literature."
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-author">
						<div class="author-info">
							<h4>Sarah Mitchell</h4>
							<p>Literature Professor, Boston University</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="testimonial">
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							"As an independent author, I appreciate how Akboheim bridges the gap between academic discourse and accessible writing. Their educational resources have helped me improve my craft while their cultural essays inspire new creative directions."
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-author">
						<div class="author-info">
							<h4>Marcus Rodriguez</h4>
							<p>Independent Author, Miami</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="testimonial">
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							"The cultural analysis on Akboheim consistently challenges my perspectives in the best way possible. Their writers tackle complex social issues with nuance and intellectual honesty that's rare in today's media landscape."
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-author">
						<div class="author-info">
							<h4>Dr. Elena Chen</h4>
							<p>Cultural Anthropologist, UCLA</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="testimonial">
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							"I've been following Akboheim for two years now, and it has fundamentally changed how I approach reading. Their educational content on literary techniques and historical context has enriched my understanding of everything I read."
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-author">
						<div class="author-info">
							<h4>James Thompson</h4>
							<p>High School English Teacher, Seattle</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="testimonial">
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							"As a book club organizer, I often turn to Akboheim for discussion topics and insights. Their reviews provide perfect conversation starters that go beyond plot summary to explore deeper themes and literary significance."
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-author">
						<div class="author-info">
							<h4>Linda Park</h4>
							<p>Book Club Coordinator, Chicago</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="testimonial">
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							"The Miami cultural perspective that Akboheim brings to literary discussions is refreshing and necessary. They understand how local and global cultures intersect in ways that feel authentic and relevant."
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-author">
						<div class="author-info">
							<h4>Carlos Mendez</h4>
							<p>Cultural Studies Student, University of Miami</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="testimonial">
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							"Akboheim's commitment to classical literature while engaging with contemporary issues creates a unique reading experience. Their essays remind us why great literature remains relevant to modern life."
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-author">
						<div class="author-info">
							<h4>Rebecca Walsh</h4>
							<p>Classics Scholar, Oxford University</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="testimonial">
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							"As a librarian, I recommend Akboheim to patrons looking for intelligent literary content. Their educational resources are particularly valuable for students and lifelong learners seeking to deepen their literary knowledge."
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-author">
						<div class="author-info">
							<h4>Michael Foster</h4>
							<p>Head Librarian, Denver Public Library</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="testimonial">
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							"The author interviews on Akboheim provide insights I can't find anywhere else. They ask thoughtful questions that reveal the creative process and intellectual journey behind the books we love."
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-author">
						<div class="author-info">
							<h4>Amanda Liu</h4>
							<p>Literary Agent, New York</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="testimonial">
					<div class="testimonial-content">
						<p class="testimonial-text">
							"Akboheim represents everything I want in literary journalism: intellectual rigor without pretension, cultural awareness without agenda, and a genuine love for the written word that shines through every article."
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-author">
						<div class="author-info">
							<h4>Robert Anderson</h4>
							<p>Retired Professor of English, Yale University</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<section class="cta-section">
				<h2>Share Your Story</h2>
				<p>
					Have thoughts about Akboheim? We'd love to hear from you. Your perspective matters to our community.
				</p>
				<div class="cta-buttons">
					<a href="/contact" class="cta-btn primary">Contact Us</a>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-container {
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 40px 24px;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #1a1a1a;
	}

	.page-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 48px;
		padding-bottom: 24px;
		border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
		font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 48px);
		font-weight: 900;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
		margin: 0 0 12px;
		color: #1a1a1a;
	}

	.page-subtitle {
		font-family: 'Crimson Text', 'Georgia', serif;
		font-size: 20px;
		color: #666;
		margin: 0;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.page-content {
		font-family: 'Crimson Text', 'Georgia', serif;
		font-size: 17px;
	}

	.page-content p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.page-content a {
		color: #8b0000;
		text-decoration: underline;
		text-underline-offset: 2px;
	}

	.page-content a:hover {
		color: #a52a2a;
	}

	section {
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	section h2 {
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
		font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 36px);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		margin: 0 0 2rem;
		color: #1a1a1a;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.testimonials-grid {
		display: grid;
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	@media (min-width: 768px) {
		.testimonials-grid {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		}
	}

	@media (min-width: 1024px) {
		.testimonials-grid {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
			gap: 3rem;
		}
	}

	.testimonial {
		padding: 2rem;
		background: rgba(248, 248, 248, 0.5);
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
		position: relative;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.testimonial:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		border-color: rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}

	.testimonial::before {
		content: '"';
		position: absolute;
		top: 1rem;
		left: 1.5rem;
		font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
		font-size: 4rem;
		color: rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.2);
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.testimonial-content {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.testimonial-text {
		font-family: 'Crimson Text', 'Georgia', serif;
		font-size: 17px;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #333;
		margin: 0;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.testimonial-author {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: flex-end;
		padding-left: 2rem;
	}

	.author-info {
		text-align: right;
	}

	.author-info h4 {
		font-family: 'Inter', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
		font-size: 16px;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		color: #1a1a1a;
		margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
	}

	.author-info p {
		font-family: 'Inter', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
		font-size: 14px;
		color: #666;
		margin: 0;
		font-style: normal;
	}

	.cta-section {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 3rem 2rem;
		background: rgba(248, 248, 248, 0.3);
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
	}

	.cta-section h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.cta-section p {
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto 2rem;
		color: #555;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.cta-btn {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 14px 28px;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-family: 'Inter', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
		font-size: 16px;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.02em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
		border: 2px solid transparent;
		min-width: 160px;
	}

	.cta-btn.primary {
		background: #8b0000;
		color: white !important;
	}

	.cta-btn.primary:hover {
		background: #a52a2a;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.3);
		color: white !important;
	}

	.cta-btn.secondary {
		background: transparent;
		color: #8b0000;
		border-color: #8b0000;
	}

	.cta-btn.secondary:hover {
		background: #8b0000;
		color: white;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.page-container {
			padding: 24px 16px;
		}

		.page-header {
			margin-bottom: 32px;
		}

		.page-header h1 {
			margin-bottom: 8px;
		}

		.page-content {
			font-size: 16px;
		}

		.testimonials-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		.testimonial {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}

		.testimonial-text {
			font-size: 16px;
		}

		.cta-section {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}

		.cta-btn {
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 280px;
		}
	}
</style>
